{"word":"H6299 - פָּדָה - pâdâh - paw-daw' - [idiom] at all","slug":"H6299","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">פָּדָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pâdâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>paw-daw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] at all"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05D3;&#x05D4; - pa&#x0302;da&#x0302;h</b> - <i>paw-daw'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>sever</i>, that is, <i>ransom</i>; generally to <i>release</i>, <i>preserve: - </i> X at all, deliver, X by any means, ransom, (that are to be, let be) redeem (-ed), rescue, X surely."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6300\">H6300</a>, <a href=\"#/H6301\">H6301</a>, <a href=\"#/H6302\">H6302</a>, <a href=\"#/H6303\">H6303</a>, <a href=\"#/H6304\">H6304</a>, <a href=\"#/H6305\">H6305</a>, <a href=\"#/H6306\">H6306</a>, <a href=\"#/H6307\">H6307</a>"}]}